{"word":"συνάγω","slug":"συνάγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συνάγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄγω\">ἄγω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘bring together in a collective manner’, <b>gather<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of things <b><a href='B:470 3:12'>Mt 3:12</a>; <a href='B:470 6:26'>6:26</a>; <a href='B:470 12:30'>12:30</a>; <a href='B:470 13:30'>13:30</a>; <a href='B:470 25:24'>25:24</a>; <a href='B:490 3:17'>Lk 3:17</a>; <a href='B:490 15:13'>15:13</a></b> (turn into cash is debatable); <b><a href='B:500 4:36'>J 4:36</a>; <a href='B:500 6:12'>6:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of humans<b> <a href='B:470 13:2'>Mt 13:2</a>; <a href='B:470 22:10'>22:10</a>; <a href='B:470 25:32'>25:32</a>; <a href='B:480 4:1'>Mk 4:1</a>; <a href='B:500 11:47'>J 11:47</a>; <a href='B:510 4:27'>Ac 4:27</a>; <a href='B:730 16:14'>Rv 16:14</a>; <a href='B:730 20:8'>20:8</a>;</b> <el>ἐπὶ τὸ αὐτό</el> <b><a href='B:470 22:34'>Mt 22:34</a>; <a href='B:510 4:26'>Ac 4:26</a>;</b> as collective <b><a href='B:510 13:44'>13:44</a>.</b> Pass. <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> sense <b><a href='B:500 18:2'>J 18:2</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘include with others as guest’, <b>take in as guest <a href='B:470 25:35'>Mt 25:35</a>, <a href='B:470 25:38'>38</a>, <a href='B:470 25:43'>43</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> some aspect of guest status surfaces in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> use, apparently in sense of ‘come into the company of others’, <b>join in,</b> <el>σύναγε <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔτι\">ἔτι</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνω\">ἄνω</a></el> join a bit higher up <b><a href='B:470 20:28'>Mt 20:28</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συναγαγεῖν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συναγωγή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}